lgp.core.evolution.population

Class MutationOperator<T>

  • lgp.core.evolution.population.MutationOperator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of programs being mutated.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MacroMutationOperator, MicroMutationOperator

    public class MutationOperator<T>
implements Module

    A search operator used during evolution to mutate an individual from a population.

    The individual is mutated in place, that is a call to MutationOperator.mutate will directly modify the given individual.
